Apa, tanpa halangan?

00:53:26.349 --> 00:53:27.684
Bagaimana awak tahu?

00:53:27.767 --> 00:53:29.561
Kawan baru saya memberitahu saya.

00:53:30.186 --> 00:53:33.565
Namanya Oh Seung-taek.
Kalian mungkin kenal dia.

00:53:42.282 --> 00:53:43.116
rasa berasap ni.

